quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  91,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  91,1,Sooraj aur uss ki dhoop ki qasam
  91,2,aur chaand ki qasam jabkay woh uss ke peechay aata hai
  91,3,aur din ki qasam jabkay woh ( Sooraj ko ) numaya kar deta hai
  91,4,aur raat ki qasam jabkay woh ( Sooraj ko ) dhaank layti hai
  91,5,aur aasman ki aur uss zaat ki qasam jis ne ussay qaim kya
  91,6,aur zameen ki aur uss zaat ki qasam jis ne ussay bichhaya
  91,7,aur nafs insani ki aur uss zaat ki qasam jis ne ussay hamwar kya
  91,8,phir uss ki badi aur uss ki parhaiz gari is par ilham kar di
  91,9,yaqeenan Falah pa gaya woh jis ne nafs ka tazkia kya
  91,10,aur namuraad howa woh jis ne uss ko daba diya
  91,11,samood ne apni sar kashi ki bana par jhtlaya
  91,12,jab uss qoum ka sab se ziyada shaqqi aadmi biphar kar utha
  91,13,"to Allah ke rasool ne unn logon se kaha ke khabardaar, Allah ki oontni ko ( haath nah lagana ) aur iss ke pani peenay ( mein Maney nah hona )"
  91,14,magar unhon ne uss ki baat ko jhoota qarar diya aur oontni ko maar dala aakhir kaar unn ke gunah ki Padaash mein un ke Rab ne un par aisi aafat tori ke aik sath sab ko pewand khaak kar diya
  91,15,aur usay ( apne a seen feal ke ) kisi buray nateejay ka koi khauf nahi hai
